main event: Several citizens of Stillwater, Minnesota observed a large white light or object hovering in the sky on February 6, 1967.
interesting points: The object appeared to be giving off a bright white light.
The object remained in the sky for several minutes before suddenly disappearing.
The sighting was reported by multiple witnesses in Stillwater, Minnesota.
The object was described as hovering at a high altitude.
The report states that this case is not considered an unusual sighting.
sighted object: a large white light or object
